capitalism.editor.model

Class EditableTimeStamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • capitalism.editor.model.EditableTimeStamp

  • public class EditableTimeStamp
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the editable information copied from a persistent timeStamp record. After editing, it is saved back to a new persistent timeStamp record. TODO write an editor page for the timeStamp. At present, the existing persistent data is merely copied in and out.
    Author:
    afree
